Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.79,0:00:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.04,0:01:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music concludes]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.54,0:01:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,ASSAULT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.60,0:01:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Regarding Naomi Misora's disappearance,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.14,0:01:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,shouldn't we open\Nan investigation into this matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.37,0:01:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuzaki] If we do, it should be\Ncoordinated separately from the Kira case.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.43,0:01:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, we'll have to use police sketches\Ninstead of actual photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.57,0:01:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We're talking about someone who's been\Nmissing for four months already.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.28,0:01:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Chances are she's probably dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.90,0:01:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're right about that,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.41,0:02:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I find it odd\Nthat we haven't found her body yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.16,0:02:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If we did, it might provide us\Nwith some much-needed physical evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.49,0:02:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[door opens]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.58,0:02:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Watari] Ryuzaki.\N-Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.33,0:02:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Something seems to be happening\Non Sakura TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.75,0:02:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.92,0:02:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,all of the reporters and staff here\Nare Kira's hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.46,0:02:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Aside from that,\Nwe have a professional obligation…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.59,0:02:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,MESSAGE FROM KIRA\NFOUR VIDEOS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.18,0:02:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,…to share this message with you.\NI assure you that this is not a hoax.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.43,0:02:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And that Sakura TV is not airing this tape\Nfor the purposes of sensationalism.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.93,0:02:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] "Kira's hostages"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.39,0:02:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.23,0:02:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[man on TV] Four days ago,\Nour program director here at Sakura TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.15,0:02:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,received four tapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.56,0:02:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,After a thorough examination,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.15,0:02:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,there can be no doubt\Nthat they are from Kira himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.82,0:02:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[Demegawa] Our audience ratings\Nshould go up sixty…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.32,0:02:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,no, more like seventy percent\Nafter this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.37,0:02:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[man on TV] The first tape we received\Ncontained a prediction
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,regarding the time of death\Nof two suspected criminals
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.75,0:02:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,who'd recently been arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And as predicted,\Nat the exact time that Kira had specified,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,both men died suddenly of heart attacks\Nyesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.46,0:02:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuzaki] If what they're saying is true,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.21,0:02:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,it's clearly something\Nthat only Kira could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.18,0:03:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[man on TV] Kira has instructed us\Nto air the second tape today
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.14,0:03:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,at exactly 5:59 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And we do intend\Nto comply with his demands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.97,0:03:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This tape should offer proof of his powers\Nby predicting yet another death.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.98,0:03:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond that, we understand\Nthat it contains a message
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.31,0:03:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,to all the people of the world from Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.48,0:03:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] This has to be another fake,\Ndon't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.44,0:03:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.57,0:03:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure even Sakura TV\Nwouldn't stoop that low.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.66,0:03:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, the video.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kira clears throat]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kira] I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If this video was being aired\Non April 18th,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,at exactly 5:59 PM, as I requested,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.38,0:03:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,then the time now is 5:59:47, 48, 49…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.01,0:03:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Please change the channel to Taiyo TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The news anchor, Mr. Kazuhiko Hibima,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,will die of a heart attack\Nat exactly six o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.77,0:03:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-What?\N-Change it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.27,0:03:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,TAIYO TV
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.57,0:03:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.78,0:04:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[TV staff shouting indistinctly]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.53,0:04:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How could he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Change the channel back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.24,0:04:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-And I need you to bring us another TV.\N-[Kira] Mr. Hibima continued to refer…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.53,0:04:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-Watari. No, make it two.\N-[Kira] …to Kira as evil on air.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Watari] Yes.\N-[Kira] This is punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.25,0:04:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kira] I'll present you\Nwith another victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My next target is NHN TV commentator,\NMr. Seiji Kumaizumi,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.30,0:04:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,who is scheduled to appear\Nin a live broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.88,0:04:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He too has dared to defy Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Matsuda] R-- Ryuzaki!\N-Change it to Channel 24!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.05,0:04:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[TV staff shouting indistinctly]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuzaki] Please, change it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.31,0:04:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kira] Now that you have seen\Nproof of my powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.56,0:04:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,you should have no trouble believing\Nthat I'm Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.56,0:04:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuzaki] Kira said that he was going to\Nsend a message to the people of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.82,0:04:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] Stop this broadcast!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.40,0:04:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-We can't let him finish!\N-[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.11,0:04:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ukita] Get Sakura TV on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.78,0:04:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.83,0:04:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying but none of my contacts\Nat the station have their phones on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.41,0:04:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody is picking up\Nat the reception either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.17,0:04:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts] Ukita!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.88,0:04:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stop that broadcast myself,\Nif that's what it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.80,0:05:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kira] People of the world,\Nplease listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The last thing I want to do\Nis kill the innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate evil and love justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.06,0:05:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always thought of the police\Nas allies, and not as enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Kira…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.52,0:05:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-[siren wailing]\N-[Kira] I intend to create a new world,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.73,0:05:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,a perfect world that is free from evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.32,0:05:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If you agree to join me in my mission,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.15,0:05:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I know we can make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.11,0:05:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And as long as no one tries to catch me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.28,0:05:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise that the innocent will not die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.53,0:05:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.08,0:05:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kira] Even if you don't agree with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.16,0:05:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,all I ask is that you do not publicize\Nyour views in the media.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.79,0:05:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-If you can do that, you will be spared.\N-[people whispering indistinctly]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.63,0:05:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All you have to do now is be patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.92,0:05:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I will create a better world\Nthat we can all enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.26,0:05:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Say goodbye to the world as you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon, we will have a new world\Nruled by benevolence,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.85,0:05:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,inhabited by kindhearted, honest people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.77,0:05:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to imagine it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A world where the police and I--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.98,0:06:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sachiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.19,0:06:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling, this can't be good\Nfor your health.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, you have to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sachiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Like it or not, I'm still in charge\Nof the Kira Task Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.92,0:06:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.50,0:06:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-[tires screeching]\N-[siren wailing]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.26,0:06:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ukita panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.09,0:06:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ukita] Damn it! It's locked!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.35,0:06:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.02,0:06:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.56,0:06:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-[heart beating loudly]\N-[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.48,0:06:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.32,0:06:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Aizawa] Hello?\N-[reporter] We interrupt
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-this program to bring you live…\N-Damn, I'm still not getting through!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.92,0:07:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,-[reporter] …outside Sakura TV studio.\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.21,0:07:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Aizawa! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.71,0:07:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,SAKURA TV
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.97,0:07:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[reporter] As you can see, someone\Nhas collapsed just outside the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Again, we're coming to you live\Nfrom the Sakura TV building!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.22,0:07:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] Ukita!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.89,0:07:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.65,0:07:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts] Mr. Aizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.78,0:07:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.65,0:07:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you think?\NI've got to go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.99,0:07:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuzaki] You can't.\NPlease, think about it rationally.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You want me\Nto just sit here and watch TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.99,0:07:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuzaki]\NIf this truly is the work of Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.79,0:07:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll just meet the same fate\Nif you go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.57,0:07:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You told us\Nthat Kira couldn't kill without a name!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how could this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.21,0:07:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The aliases and fake police IDs\Nwere worthless!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.76,0:07:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do, L?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think Kira has\Nall our names already, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.71,0:07:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a definite possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:07:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,However, if that's the case,\Nyou'd think it would be easier for him
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.52,0:08:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,to kill off the entire task force\Nbefore making a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Initially, I deduced that Kira needed\Nboth the name and the face to kill,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but from what we've just seen,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.36,0:08:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say it's not entirely impossible\Nthat Kira can kill with only a face.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.28,0:08:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All I know for sure is that Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,is either in that TV station,\Nor he's somewhere close by.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,In a place where he can watch\Neveryone who enters the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-Perhaps--\N-If Kira is in the area,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.29,0:08:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,then isn't that why\Nwe should get down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuzaki] For all we know,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,he could've just placed\Nsurveillance cameras in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If we rush down there unprepared,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.80,0:08:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-all of us will be killed.\N-Wasn't it you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.26,0:08:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,who said we would have to\Nrisk our life to catch Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I meant what I said, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,risking my life to catch Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.89,0:08:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and doing something\Nthat I know will cost me my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,are two entirely different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.73,0:08:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, control yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We've lost Ukita.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.07,0:08:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand you wanna go there,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,but if something was to happen\Nto you as well…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.91,0:09:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kira] I now await\Na response from the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You must decide whether or not
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.71,0:09:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you will help me create\Na better world for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.04,0:09:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Please announce your decision\Non the six o'clock news in four days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.88,0:09:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I prepared two videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.30,0:09:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,One to be aired if the answer is "yes,"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.59,0:09:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and another if the answer is "no."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.35,0:09:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.93,0:09:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.72,0:09:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[police siren wailing]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.06,0:09:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.02,0:09:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.23,0:09:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[man screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.57,0:09:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.83,0:09:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.74,0:09:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Step out of the vehicle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.67,0:09:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kira video.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.83,0:09:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me which studio\Nthey are broadcasting it from.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[reporter] A vehicle has just driven\Nthrough the front doors of the station!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.80,0:09:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's one way\Nof getting into the building
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:09:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,without being seen by Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] But who would…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.60,0:10:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop this broadcast immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand those tapes over to me!\NDo you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[Demegawa] Hold on, officer!\NIt's not that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.31,0:10:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,My hands are tied here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.73,0:10:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If we stop this broadcast,\Nhe will kill all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna be killed right here and now\Nif you don't give those tapes to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha-- Come on!\NWhat the hell do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.28,0:10:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is happening because you chose\Nto make Kira a celebrity!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're getting exactly what you deserve!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.94,0:10:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-[gasping]\N-I want every single copy you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.81,0:10:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't make me ask you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[Demegawa] I-- I got it!\NI'll give them to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.53,0:10:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem. Just please,\Nstop waving that gun around!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.57,0:11:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're acting like a madman!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.57,0:11:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[siren wailing]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[reporter gasps]\NWe're still outside Sakura TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.91,0:11:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see,\Na police car has just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.24,0:11:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we are not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.75,0:11:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There're still other officers out there
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,who are willing to stand up to Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.50,0:11:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Ryuzaki] Mr. Aizawa.\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.75,0:11:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You know Deputy Director Kitamura's\Ncell phone number, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.05,0:11:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[ringing]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.68,0:11:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Aizawa, I told you not to call me\Non this phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-[L] This is L.\N-[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.51,0:11:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I need you to do for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There may be police officers\Nwho'll see this broadcast
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.39,0:11:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and feel moved to take action\Nin the name of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.48,0:11:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't take control\Nof the situation quickly,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.65,0:11:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,there will be a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.15,0:11:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But technically, we are not supposed\Nto be involved in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.83,0:11:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.03,0:11:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[reporter] Two police officers\Nhave just collapsed on the sidewalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.53,0:11:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we may be in danger!\NWe are moving away from the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.37,0:11:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand, L.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see your point now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me what I should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[phone ringing]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.22,0:12:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective Superintendent Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.97,0:12:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Call him back immediately,\Nand give me the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.84,0:12:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to speak with Ryuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.31,0:12:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.60,0:12:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Yagami, so you're the one\Ndriving the police van.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.77,0:12:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NI couldn't just sit and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've confiscated all of the tapes.\NI'm bringing them to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.61,0:12:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But what about your condition?\NAre you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.11,0:12:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm feeling just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest with you,\NI don't think I've ever felt more alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.41,0:12:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what do you think I should do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.53,0:12:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I take going out the front\Nwould be too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.12,0:12:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But I could always\Nuse the police van again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.37,0:12:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, hold the line for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Deputy Director Kitamura,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.92,0:12:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,it was Chief Yagami\Nwho just drove into the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.38,0:12:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are your preparations complete?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's done, as you requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.51,0:12:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Yagami, listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.80,0:12:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,In exactly five minutes, I want you\Nto come out the front entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.39,0:12:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me\Nto exit through the front entrance?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.23,0:13:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[footsteps echoing]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.66,0:13:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.67,0:13:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[police officer]\NMake sure there are no gaps!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not reveal your faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.84,0:13:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We know that Kira is not in the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.17,0:13:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He's outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.06,0:13:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.81,0:13:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll drive myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.77,0:13:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ide] I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.91,0:13:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[police officer] Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.12,0:13:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a very good chance that Kira\Nis still in the vicinity of the station!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:13:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,As you move out, proceed with caution.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.54,0:13:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not to remove your helmets!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.63,0:14:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[Koki] There you have it.\NThe police refuse to cooperate with Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.96,0:14:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, they're preparing to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.88,0:14:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And as much\Nas I fear for my own life in saying so,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.43,0:14:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,this is right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.56,0:14:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And it must be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.72,0:14:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira has become a threat\Nto our very constitution.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.10,0:14:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And as citizens, we must fight back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.56,0:14:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I am NHN's Golden News anchor,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.57,0:14:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Koki Tanakabara!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.82,0:14:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-[door opens]\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.95,0:14:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-Chief Yagami!\N-[Ryuzaki] Welcome back, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.95,0:14:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts] Ryuzaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.49,0:14:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for taking matters\Ninto my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to admit,\NI got a little bit carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-No.\N-Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,These are all of the tapes\Nin an envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.25,0:14:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything Kira sent to the station\Nis in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.71,0:14:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuzaki] I can't thank you enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.30,0:14:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'd better rest for a minute.\N[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.26,0:14:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuzaki] Mr. Yagami…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This won't go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:14:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The postmark is from Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.94,0:15:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But Kira can control his victims\Nbefore they die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.86,0:15:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So, he could have delivered it from Osaka\Nwithout going there himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.15,0:15:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Aizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you please take this\Nto the crime lab right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.66,0:15:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have a couple of friends\Ndown there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.70,0:15:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure they\Ngo over every inch of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.70,0:15:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good. Please, do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,While you're doing that,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.12,0:15:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to watch these tapes\Nto see if they can tell us anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] Well, what do you make of these?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.13,0:15:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They were definitely interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If the police had said "yes,"\Nand agreed to cooperate with Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.14,0:15:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,tape number three\Nwas supposed to be aired.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Tape four if the answer was "no".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.22,0:15:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Tape three covers\Nthe terms of cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.64,0:15:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Put simply, he is requesting that\Nwe broadcast the names of more criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.61,0:15:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems particularly interested\Nin those who have assaulted others,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.94,0:15:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,or those who have somehow hurt
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,or taken advantage\Nof the weak and defenseless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.36,0:15:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, Kira would\Nplay the role of judge in all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.45,0:15:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, as proof that\Nthe police are willing to cooperate,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.88,0:16:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,he wants police officials and L\Nto appear on TV
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.00,0:16:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,to make a public announcement\Nthat we plan to cooperate with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.46,0:16:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.09,0:16:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuzaki] He needs us to reveal our faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.56,0:16:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That way, he can kill us\Nif the police do anything suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.38,0:16:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,\Nhe will hold our lives as insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.30,0:16:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.43,0:16:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what about\Nthe content of the fourth video
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.31,0:16:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,if we were to answer "no"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.10,0:16:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The wording was different\Nbut he more or less says the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.86,0:16:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Yagami, it should go without saying\Nthat the answer is "no".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, have someone take tape number four\Nover to Sakura TV
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.53,0:16:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and authorize them to broadcast it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.66,0:16:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kira] I can only say it's a shame\Nthat your answer is "no."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.99,0:16:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's clear that the police\Nwish to oppose me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.62,0:16:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This will not go unpunished.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.62,0:16:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I will start by taking the life
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,of either of the Director-General\Nof the NPA,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.34,0:16:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,or the detective known as L,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,who is currently\Nleading the investigation against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.01,0:16:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The Director-General or L.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Who will pay the price for your refusal
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:16:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,to cooperate in the creation\Nof the peaceful world?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.14,0:17:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You have four days to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.31,0:17:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles quietly]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.24,0:17:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like I've even got God\Non my side now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.29,0:17:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose it's actually
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.61,0:17:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,a God of Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.12,0:17:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles] Seems like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.48,0:17:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It would appear that another Shinigami\Nhas come to the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.27,0:17:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And somehow that Shinigami's Death Note
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.83,0:17:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,has fallen into the hands of\Nsomeone who agrees with Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.04,0:17:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And this person most likely\Nhas the Shinigami-eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,which makes him very deadly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.93,0:17:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,His power to kill surpasses even mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.76,0:17:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,One thing is for certain.\NIf I leave things,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.01,0:17:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure that L would be\Nfinished off within the next four days.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.64,0:17:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,However…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.31,0:17:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't forgive this impostor
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,for the way he's tarnishing Kira's image\Nwith these senseless killings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention,\Nif he slips up and gets caught,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.19,0:17:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the Death Note could be discovered,\Nand that I cannot allow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.99,0:17:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't afford to leave him alone\Nfor much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[cackles]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.49,0:18:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, what needs to happen very soon
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.90,0:18:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is for me to join the task force.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.29,0:18:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It will allow me to keep track of L
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.46,0:18:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and this fake Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki, I'm afraid it's as you thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.09,0:18:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Several of our member countries\Nhave weighed in
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.47,0:18:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and it seems they're in favor\Nof having the real L appear on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.44,0:18:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's the most appropriate choice\Ngiven the options.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.77,0:18:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we still have three days\Nbefore it happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.23,0:18:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we can find\Nsome countermeasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.57,0:18:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,After all of this,\Nit would really annoy me…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.42,0:18:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,if I'm killed by the first person\Nwho jumped on the Kira's bandwagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.41,0:18:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ryuzaki, what do you mean by that?\N-[swallows]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That there is a strong possibility\Nthat this Kira is a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.42,0:18:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we should think of him\Nmore as a second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A second Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.67,0:18:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I-- I don't understand.\NWhy do you think there's a copycat?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.09,0:19:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you come to that conclusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.51,0:19:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuzaki] I looked at the victims
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.14,0:19:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,he used as predictions on tape number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.26,0:19:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Their purpose was to prove\Nto Sakura TV staff that he is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.10,0:19:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Both their names were only reported\Nin tabloids and daytime talk-shows,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.44,0:19:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,so they weren't exactly\Nhardened criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The real Kira\Nhas no need to prove himself
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.24,0:19:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,using such insignificant criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.53,0:19:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But from the perspective\Nof the Second Kira…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[gulps]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.63,0:19:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd wanna make absolutely certain
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that he didn't predict\Nthe death of a criminal
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.12,0:19:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,who could be killed\Nby the real Kira first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.37,0:19:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm… Ryuzaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.38,0:19:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had to put a number on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.88,0:19:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,what's the probability of a second Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.00,0:19:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuzaki] This time, I'd say\Nit's more than 70 percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.55,0:19:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't like the way he operates.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.22,0:19:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Not like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.14,0:19:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuzaki] In the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.22,0:19:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,he has traditionally\Navoided killing innocent people,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.68,0:19:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,with the exception of those\Nwho were trying to catch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.27,0:19:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, if we can capture one Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.77,0:19:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that will provide us\Nwith a lot of insight
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.94,0:19:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,into how we can find the other one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.68,0:20:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.40,0:20:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like your permission to ask your son
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.41,0:20:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,to cooperate with us\Nin this investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.73,0:20:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want my son to join the task force,\Ndoes this mean you no longer suspect him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.16,0:20:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I can't say\Nthat he's been completely cleared,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.08,0:20:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but his deductive abilities would be\Ninvaluable to us right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.84,0:20:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] So that's what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.38,0:20:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If my son wants to cooperate with you,\Nthen I have no reason to prevent it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.14,0:20:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuzaki] I appreciate that.\NHowever…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,please don't tell him that we think\Nthis latest Kira might be a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.77,0:20:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want him to know that yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.14,0:20:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to make it appear to him\Nthat we're still chasing the same Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.86,0:20:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighing]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.31,0:20:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[Shinigami] Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.74,0:20:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave that Death Note to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.92,0:20:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,so why not use it for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.29,0:20:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] I am using it for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.71,0:20:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I believe in what Kira is doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.21,0:20:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know what kind\Nof person Kira is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.88,0:21:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to meet him and talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.19,0:21:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the only reason I sent all those\Nvideos to that TV station.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.84,0:21:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to find some way\Nto make Kira notice me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.68,0:21:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd say that probably\Ngot his attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.22,0:21:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think? [chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.68,0:21:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a dangerous game you're playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.29,0:21:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a chance you could be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.71,0:21:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] It's all right. I'm sure that Kira\Nis kind to those with pure hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.28,0:21:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And if it came down to that,\NI'm still stronger than he is
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.16,0:21:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,because I have the eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.49,0:21:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.84,0:21:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.04,0:22:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music concludes]